WEBVTT

00:01.462 --> 00:02.123
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.123 --> 00:03.504
I HAVE NOWHERE TO GO.

00:03.504 --> 00:05.926
DARLING, THERE'S REALLY NOTHING
I CAN DO TO HELP YOU NOW.

00:05.926 --> 00:06.887
I HAVE NO RESOURCES.

00:06.887 --> 00:07.718
DO YOU WORK IN FINANCE?

00:07.718 --> 00:09.180
A LITTLE BIT.

00:09.180 --> 00:10.181
HOW MUCH DO YOU HATE IT

00:10.181 --> 00:12.053
WHEN PEOPLE ASK YOU
FOR FREE ADVICE?

00:12.053 --> 00:14.725
Victoria: CONRAD LAID WASTE
TO OUR FAMILY ASSETS.

00:14.725 --> 00:15.726
LET ME HELP.

00:15.726 --> 00:16.807
CALL IT A LOAN?

00:16.807 --> 00:18.939
I LIKE TO GET OUT
AND CLEAR MY HEAD.

00:18.939 --> 00:21.232
SHOULD YOU EVER WANT
ANY COMPANY...

00:21.232 --> 00:23.694
Victoria:
DAVID, MEET YOUR DAUGHTER.

00:23.694 --> 00:25.946
[ SHOTGUN COCKS ]
 DO IT. SHOOT.

00:25.946 --> 00:27.698
END THIS WHOLE THING
RIGHT NOW.

00:27.698 --> 00:30.611
I OWE YOU SO MUCH MORE
THAN A QUICK DEATH.

00:30.611 --> 00:32.323
David:
WHAT DID SHE WANT?
 CHARLOTTE.

00:32.323 --> 00:34.155
I THOUGHT IT -- THAT
IT WAS YOU THAT SHE WAS AFTER.

00:34.155 --> 00:36.077
EMILY WANTS TO DESTROY
OUR WHOLE FAMILY.

00:39.120 --> 00:40.251
EMILY!

00:40.251 --> 00:41.832
Emily: WHO WAS THAT?
WHAT DID YOU SEE?

00:41.832 --> 00:43.254
GUY IN SWEATSHIRT
WITH A KNIFE.

00:43.254 --> 00:45.666
I BARELY SAW HIS FACE.

00:53.764 --> 00:55.015
Emily:
DO YOU SEE HIM?

00:55.015 --> 00:56.517
NO.

00:56.517 --> 00:59.600
THE SYSTEM WAS MID-REBOOT.
MOST OF THE CAMERAS WERE DOWN.

00:59.600 --> 01:01.682
THANK GOD I HEARD
THE MOTION DETECTORS.

01:01.682 --> 01:03.184
YOU COULD'VE
BEEN KILLED.

01:03.184 --> 01:03.984
I'M OKAY, NOLAN.

01:03.984 --> 01:06.687
BARELY.

01:06.687 --> 01:09.029
EMS, THERE WAS
A MAN IN YOUR ROOM

01:09.029 --> 01:10.401
WITH A KNIFE,

01:10.401 --> 01:12.783
AND HE WAS NOT AFTER
YOUR STASH OF VINTAGE CARTIER.

01:12.783 --> 01:15.156
HE WANTED BLOOD.

01:15.156 --> 01:17.077
WAIT...

01:17.077 --> 01:18.999
DO YOU THINK THIS IS WHAT
VICTORIA HAD PLANNED?

01:18.999 --> 01:21.202
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN WHY
SHE DIDN'T SHOOT ME

01:21.202 --> 01:22.413
WHEN SHE HAD THE CHANCE.

01:22.413 --> 01:24.755
OF COURSE SHE'D HIRE SOMEONE
ELSE TO DO HER DIRTY WORK.

01:24.755 --> 01:27.918
[ SIGHS ]
AT LEAST HE FAILED.

01:27.918 --> 01:29.920
YEAH.
WELL, IT'S MY MOVE NOW.

01:29.920 --> 01:30.971
NO, NO, NO, NO.

01:30.971 --> 01:32.513
NO MORE MOVES.

01:32.513 --> 01:34.054
I SAY WE TAG OUT.
LET'S CALL THE POLICE.

01:34.054 --> 01:35.176
THE POLICE? NO.

01:35.176 --> 01:37.768
ALL RIGHT.
THEN AT LEAST LET'S CALL JACK.

01:37.768 --> 01:39.220
HE'S POLICE ADJACENT.

01:39.220 --> 01:41.222
'CAUSE I AM OVER
THIS WAR WITH YOU AND VICTORIA.

01:41.222 --> 01:43.144
NOLAN, WE DON'T
CALL THE POLICE.

01:43.144 --> 01:44.024
WHY NOT?

01:45.436 --> 01:47.398
OH, BECAUSE MAYBE

01:47.398 --> 01:49.610
THE HENCHMAN WASN'T
WORKING FOR VICTORIA ALONE.

01:49.610 --> 01:52.032
MAYBE LITTLE ARSON ANNIE
WAS BEHIND THIS, TOO.

01:52.032 --> 01:53.194
SHE'S NOT MY SISTER.

01:53.194 --> 01:54.615
I PROMISED
TO HELP CHARLOTTE.

01:54.615 --> 01:56.116
I'M NOT GOING TO
SIC THE COPS ON HER.

01:56.116 --> 01:58.078
OH, WHAT? SO SHE GETS ANOTHER
SPIN ON THE MURDER WHEEL?

01:58.078 --> 01:59.119
HOW MANY?

01:59.119 --> 02:01.202
I'M GOING TO
SEARCH THE PROPERTY.

02:01.202 --> 02:04.505
YOU DO KNOW THAT THAT HOODIE
IS NOT A BULLETPROOF VEST,

02:04.505 --> 02:06.086
THAT YOU CAN DIE,

02:06.086 --> 02:08.628
AND THAT THE GIRL THAT YOU ARE
SO DESPERATELY TRYING TO SAVE

02:08.628 --> 02:11.882
WOULD LIKE TO SEE THAT HAPPEN
SOONER RATHER THAN LATER?

02:11.882 --> 02:15.135
YES, YOU MADE CHOICES
THAT HURT CHARLOTTE,

02:15.135 --> 02:17.968
AND, NO,
YOU CAN'T UNDO THEM,

02:17.968 --> 02:20.181
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO REPAY HER
WITH YOUR LIFE.

02:20.181 --> 02:23.224
I'M NOT GONNA
TURN MY BACK ON HER AGAIN.

02:23.224 --> 02:24.225
NO COPS.

02:25.726 --> 02:27.027
[ DOOR OPENS ]
 [ SIGHS ]

02:27.027 --> 02:28.229
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

02:31.031 --> 02:33.694
DAVID?

02:33.694 --> 02:35.236
DAVID!

02:38.038 --> 02:39.370
CHARLOTTE?

02:51.001 --> 02:52.092
[ GASPS ]

02:52.092 --> 02:53.294
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:53.294 --> 02:55.386
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU SCARED ME.

02:58.178 --> 03:00.931
YOU'RE HURT.

03:00.931 --> 03:02.012
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:02.012 --> 03:04.225
THE HOOD OF YOUR CAR
IS STILL WARM.

03:04.225 --> 03:05.266
DID YOU JUST GET IN?

03:05.266 --> 03:06.687
YES.

03:06.687 --> 03:08.859
IT WAS TOO LATE TO DRIVE HERE,
SO I TOOK A SUITE IN THE CITY.

03:08.859 --> 03:11.232
SO, Y-YOU GOT
SOME MONEY?

03:11.232 --> 03:13.274
ENOUGH TO LAST US
FOR A WHILE.

03:14.945 --> 03:16.817
WHERE'S CHARLOTTE?

03:16.817 --> 03:19.370
I DON'T KNOW.

03:19.370 --> 03:22.122
DAVID, YOU WERE SUPPOSED
TO STAY HERE LAST NIGHT
TO PROTECT HER.

03:22.122 --> 03:23.284
I TRIED TO.

03:23.284 --> 03:25.996
[ SIGHS ]

03:27.538 --> 03:30.090
I SNUCK INTO EMILY THORNE'S
HOUSE LAST NIGHT.

03:30.090 --> 03:31.592
WHAT?

03:34.295 --> 03:36.006
DAVID, WHAT DID YOU DO?

03:37.468 --> 03:39.049
DID YOU KILL HER?

03:40.551 --> 03:42.102
I CAME CLOSE...

03:42.102 --> 03:43.974
BUT I COULDN'T.

03:43.974 --> 03:45.306
DID SHE SEE YOU?
 NO.

03:45.306 --> 03:46.607
DID ANYONE?
 NO.

03:46.607 --> 03:47.608
ARE YOU SURE?

03:47.608 --> 03:48.689
NO ONE SAW ME.

03:48.689 --> 03:51.151
I'M SORRY.

03:51.151 --> 03:53.904
I -- I DIDN'T
MEAN TO UPSET YOU.

03:53.904 --> 03:58.068
BUT THIS IS A DIFFERENT WORLD
FROM THE ONE THAT YOU LEFT.

03:58.068 --> 04:02.032
YOUR RE-EMERGENCE
MUST BE CAREFULLY PLANNED,

04:02.032 --> 04:03.163
AND YOU'LL NEED
AN ALIBI

04:03.163 --> 04:04.325
FOR THE NIGHT
OF CONRAD'S DEATH.

04:04.325 --> 04:05.786
IF YOU COME OUT NOW,

04:05.786 --> 04:09.169
THEY'LL EXPECT AN EXPLANATION
FOR WHERE YOU'VE BEEN.

04:09.169 --> 04:10.751
DO YOU HAVE ONE?

04:13.133 --> 04:15.426
David.

04:15.426 --> 04:17.257
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

04:18.879 --> 04:22.553
ALL I WANT IS THE LIFE
YOU PROMISED ME YEARS AGO,

04:22.553 --> 04:25.145
BUT WE MUSTN'T RUSH IT.

04:29.810 --> 04:31.602
LET ME
TAKE CARE OF THINGS.

04:37.027 --> 04:38.989
YEAH.

04:38.989 --> 04:41.992
YOU'RE RIGHT.

04:41.992 --> 04:43.954
YEAH, I'M NOT
THINKING CLEARLY.

04:43.954 --> 04:46.957
GET SOME REST, MY LOVE.

05:03.223 --> 05:05.135
Nolan: EMS?

05:07.558 --> 05:09.520
UM, GOT A SEC?

05:09.520 --> 05:11.732
I WAS JUST HEADING OUT.

05:11.732 --> 05:14.194
ANOTHER WALK
IN THE WOODS?

05:17.528 --> 05:19.109
NOLAN REPORTED
A BREAK-IN LAST NIGHT.

05:19.109 --> 05:22.072
WHY DIDN'T YOU CALL?

05:22.072 --> 05:24.705
[ SIGHS ] LOOK, THE ALARM
WAS OFF AND SOMEONE GOT IN,

05:24.705 --> 05:26.707
BUT HE DIDN'T TAKE ANYTHING,
NOLAN RAN HIM OFF.

05:26.707 --> 05:28.949
IT WASN'T A BIG DEAL.

05:28.949 --> 05:30.120
YOU KNOW
I LIKE MY PRIVACY.

05:30.120 --> 05:33.754
EXCEPT THAT THE, UH,
INTRUDER HAD A KNIFE, EMS.

05:33.754 --> 05:35.085
Hunter:
WELL, THAT ESCALATES THIS

05:35.085 --> 05:37.548
FROM BREAKING AND ENTERING
TO AGGRAVATED ASSAULT.

05:37.548 --> 05:40.551
SO, WE'RE GONNA NEED
A STATEMENT.

05:42.302 --> 05:45.015
HUMOR US, SINCE I'VE ALREADY
GOT MY PAD OUT.

06:48.328 --> 06:49.700
[ GRUNTING LOUDLY ]

06:54.995 --> 06:58.168
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

06:58.168 --> 07:00.170
[ YELLS ]

07:02.593 --> 07:03.544
[ GRUNTS ]

07:04.845 --> 07:06.136
[ SCREAMS ]

07:15.936 --> 07:18.148
♪ TO FEEL IT IN MY BLOOD,
LOVE ♪

07:18.148 --> 07:19.690
JUST LET THEM KNOW
I'M NOT HERE.

07:19.690 --> 07:22.022
THEY CAN REACH ME ON MY CELL
IF THEY REALLY WANT TO,

07:22.022 --> 07:24.114
BUT, UM, I DON'T
NEED TO HAVE THIS --
 OKAY.

07:24.114 --> 07:25.526
MORNING.
 DANIEL.

07:25.526 --> 07:26.617
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:26.617 --> 07:28.158
MERCI.

07:28.158 --> 07:31.201
I THOUGHT WE WERE MEETING LATER
AT YOUR PLACE.

07:31.201 --> 07:36.957
YEAH, WELL, MY PLACE ISN'T
EXACTLY MY PLACE ANYMORE.

07:36.957 --> 07:39.039
THE RIPLEY'S TOO EXPENSIVE
FOR ME RIGHT NOW.

07:39.039 --> 07:43.003
THE TRUTH IS, MY FAMILY'S
ASSETS ARE DEPLETED.

07:43.003 --> 07:44.214
DANIEL --

07:44.214 --> 07:46.296
AND BEFORE YOU OFFER,
I'LL BE OKAY, ALL RIGHT?

07:46.296 --> 07:48.679
I'M A GRAYSON --
I'VE SURVIVED WORSE.

07:48.679 --> 07:49.850
I KNOW YOU WILL.

07:49.850 --> 07:51.141
BUT I NEED TO TELL YOU

07:51.141 --> 07:54.094
THAT YOUR MOTHER
CAME TO SEE ME LAST NIGHT.

07:54.094 --> 07:55.225
HUH.

07:55.225 --> 07:58.649
SHE ALREADY TOLD YOU ABOUT
OUR FINANCIAL SITUATION.

07:58.649 --> 08:00.651
WHAT DID SHE WANT?

08:00.651 --> 08:01.942
A LOAN.

08:01.942 --> 08:04.565
I'M SORRY SHE PUT YOU
IN SUCH AN AWKWARD POSITION.

08:04.565 --> 08:06.987
AWKWARD?

08:06.987 --> 08:10.110
[ SIGHS ] WELL, I TRULY
BELIEVE MY FATHER LOVED HER.

08:10.110 --> 08:13.574
BESIDES,
NOW SHE OWES ME.

08:13.574 --> 08:15.916
NOW, THAT'S A HELL OF A CARD
TO HAVE IN YOUR HAND.

08:15.916 --> 08:16.957
MM-HMM.

08:16.957 --> 08:18.669
HOW DO YOU SAY
"BADASS" IN FRENCH?

08:18.669 --> 08:20.711
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M NOT SURE IF I QUALIFY.

08:20.711 --> 08:22.382
I MAY HAVE HANDLED
YOUR MOTHER,

08:22.382 --> 08:24.625
BUT THE QUARTERLY EARNINGS
ARE DOWN AGAIN.

08:24.625 --> 08:27.087
WELL, I CAN TAKE A LOOK
AT THE NUMBERS IF YOU WANT.

08:27.087 --> 08:30.801
IT'S A CONTENT ISSUE.
THAT'S WHAT DRIVES THE NUMBERS.

08:30.801 --> 08:34.014
AND THE EDITORIAL DEPARTMENT
IS LACKING, SO...

08:34.014 --> 08:36.767
HEY, YOU SHOULDN'T BE
WORRYING ABOUT ME TODAY.

08:36.767 --> 08:38.808
WHAT TIME IS YOUR MEETING
WITH, UH...?

08:38.808 --> 08:39.809
LOUISE ELLIS?

08:39.809 --> 08:42.102
YES.
 AT NOON.

08:42.102 --> 08:45.235
AFTER DRINKS LAST NIGHT,
I WAS UP FOR HOURS

08:45.235 --> 08:48.909
COMING UP WITH A STRATEGY
TO EXPAND HER PORTFOLIO.

08:48.909 --> 08:52.613
I MEAN, MANAGING A MEMBER
OF ONE OF THE SOUTH'S
MOST PROMINENT FAMILIES

08:52.613 --> 08:55.205
WOULD BE THE PERFECT START
FOR MY WEALTH-MANAGEMENT FIRM.

08:55.205 --> 08:59.039
WELL, THIS LOUISE
WOULD BE A FOOL NOT TO HIRE YOU.

08:59.039 --> 09:01.081
YOU CAN BE
VERY CHARMING.

09:01.081 --> 09:02.252
HMM.

09:02.252 --> 09:04.164
I HOPE SO.

09:04.164 --> 09:07.007
I FEEL LIKE I'M STARTING
MY LIFE OVER FROM SCRATCH.

09:08.258 --> 09:09.800
I REALLY NEED THIS TO WORK.

09:13.173 --> 09:15.225
THEN MAKE IT WORK...

09:15.225 --> 09:18.438
BECAUSE THAT'S
WHAT WE DO.

09:18.438 --> 09:20.520
MM.
 MM.

09:22.813 --> 09:24.945
DAMN RIGHT.

09:24.945 --> 09:27.948
SO, YOU WOKE UP WHEN YOU HEARD
MR. ROSS YELL YOUR NAME.

09:27.948 --> 09:30.741
AND YOU SAW THE INTRUDER --
WHITE MALE, MEDIUM BUILD --

09:30.741 --> 09:32.572
STANDING OVER YOU
WITH A KNIFE.

09:32.572 --> 09:34.825
NOW, DID YOU GET A LOOK
AT HIS FACE?

09:34.825 --> 09:36.827
I COULD BARELY
MAKE OUT ANYTHING

09:36.827 --> 09:38.869
BEFORE HE JUMPED
OFF THE BALCONY.

09:38.869 --> 09:42.082
THAT'S GOT TO BE
A 15-FOOT DROP AT LEAST.

09:42.082 --> 09:43.333
MY GUESS IS,
THE GUY HURT HIMSELF.

09:43.333 --> 09:46.206
DO YOU MIND IF I TAKE A LOOK
AT THE JUMP SITE?

09:46.206 --> 09:48.208
I'LL DO THE HONORS,
OFFICER HUNTER.

09:48.208 --> 09:49.209
IT'S RIGHT THIS WAY.

09:53.473 --> 09:55.055
EMILY --
 Emily:
DON'T, JACK.

09:55.055 --> 09:57.427
I'M NOT INVOLVING YOU ANY MORE
THAN NOLAN ALREADY HAS.

09:57.427 --> 09:59.059
SO I'M RIGHT TO SUSPECT
THAT THERE'S MORE HERE,

09:59.059 --> 10:00.681
AND, WHAT, I'M SUPPOSED
TO JUST BACK OFF?

10:00.681 --> 10:02.182
IT WAS
A SIMPLE BREAK-IN.

10:03.934 --> 10:05.025
LOOK, THE FIRE
WAS ONE THING.

10:05.025 --> 10:07.317
I LET YOU STAND BY YOUR
STATEMENT TO PROTECT CHARLOTTE.

10:07.317 --> 10:09.229
Jack: BUT IF -- IF THIS IS
WHAT I THINK IT IS,

10:09.229 --> 10:10.991
IT'S MURDER FOR HIRE.

10:10.991 --> 10:13.233
ARE YOU DONE
MAKING YOUR STATEMENT?

10:13.233 --> 10:15.615
CHARLOTTE IS
OUT OF YOUR CONTROL.

10:15.615 --> 10:18.198
YOU CAN'T MAKE
THE PEOPLE YOU LOVE CHANGE,

10:18.198 --> 10:20.580
EVEN IF IT'S FOR
THEIR OWN GOOD.

10:23.243 --> 10:25.205
NOW, IF THIS THING
IS TIED TO VICTORIA

10:25.205 --> 10:26.747
AND IF WE CAN FIND
THE INTRUDER,

10:26.747 --> 10:29.459
WE CAN TAKE HER DOWN
LEGITIMATELY AND MAYBE
EVEN SAVE CHARLOTTE.

10:29.459 --> 10:30.961
BUT WHAT YOU'RE DOING
TO HELP HER,

10:30.961 --> 10:32.713
IT'S -- IT'S NOT WORKING,
AND YOU'RE IN DANGER.

10:32.713 --> 10:35.926
JACK --
 CAN YOU PLEASE
JUST LET ME DO MY JOB?

10:38.018 --> 10:39.429
I CAN'T STOP YOU.

10:39.429 --> 10:40.721
NO, YOU CAN'T.

10:44.064 --> 10:47.818
[ SIGHS ] AND, EMILY...

10:47.818 --> 10:50.650
IF VICTORIA TURNS UP
HURT...

10:50.650 --> 10:52.773
OR WORSE...

10:52.773 --> 10:54.234
I WILL ARREST YOU.

11:03.163 --> 11:04.664
[ DOOR CLOSES, KEYS JINGLE ]

11:04.664 --> 11:07.708
MY SUPER
NEEDS TO BE FIRED.

11:07.708 --> 11:09.339
I SPOKE TO DR. HICKS.

11:09.339 --> 11:12.632
YOU POLISHED OFF
AN OLD PRESCRIPTION OF MY XANAX

11:12.632 --> 11:14.134
AND THEN HAD IT REFILLED.

11:14.134 --> 11:16.556
WHY ARE YOU GOING DOWN
THIS UGLY ROAD AGAIN?

11:16.556 --> 11:18.428
ARE YOU SERIOUSLY
ASKING ME THAT?

11:18.428 --> 11:21.011
WE HAVE ALL
BEEN TO HELL AND BACK.

11:21.011 --> 11:22.723
YEAH, MINE
WAS A ONE-WAY TRIP.

11:22.723 --> 11:26.356
I JUST FOUND OUT EMILY IS AMANDA
AND MY FATHER IS ALIVE.

11:26.356 --> 11:27.768
EXACTLY --
HE IS ALIVE,

11:27.768 --> 11:30.310
AND YOUR REACTION IS TO HIDE
BEHIND A HAZE OF PILLS.

11:30.310 --> 11:31.191
NO.

11:31.191 --> 11:32.903
MY REACTION
WAS HAPPINESS.

11:32.903 --> 11:34.114
BUT YOU RUINED THAT

11:34.114 --> 11:36.276
AND MADE MEETING MY FATHER
ALL ABOUT HURTING EMILY.

11:36.276 --> 11:40.080
WHAT DO YOU REALLY
WANT FROM ME, MOM?

11:40.080 --> 11:42.242
NOTHING BUT
TO SEE YOU HAPPY.

11:42.242 --> 11:44.454
[ SIGHS ]

11:44.454 --> 11:47.878
THE GRAYSON MANTRA --
LIE AND DENY.

11:47.878 --> 11:49.499
I'M SICK OF IT.

11:49.499 --> 11:51.671
I DO WANT A RELATIONSHIP
WITH MY FATHER,

11:51.671 --> 11:53.924
BUT NOT IF YOU'RE GONNA BE
CONTROLLING IT.

11:53.924 --> 11:57.217
YOU ARE NOT A VICTIM, SO
STOP CHOOSING TO ACT LIKE ONE.

11:57.217 --> 12:00.640
NOW, IF YOU WANT A RELATIONSHIP
WITH YOUR FATHER, FIGHT FOR IT.

12:00.640 --> 12:02.973
AND IF YOU WANT MY RESPECT,
THEN EARN IT.

12:02.973 --> 12:05.055
BUT DO NOT GIVE IN
TO THE DARKNESS

12:05.055 --> 12:07.057
THAT WILL DESTROY YOU.

12:23.033 --> 12:25.455
I MEAN, FIRST THE FIRE
AND THEN THIS?

12:25.455 --> 12:30.000
WHAT DID SHE DO,
WALK UNDER A LADDER
 AND BREAK A MIRROR?
 [ CHUCKLES ]

12:30.000 --> 12:32.292
YOU NEVER MENTIONED THAT
YOU RAN INTO EMILY YESTERDAY.

12:32.292 --> 12:35.505
YEAH. OUT BY
THE OLD WINDMILL SITE.

12:35.505 --> 12:38.428
SHE SAID
SHE WAS OUT FOR A WALK.

12:38.428 --> 12:40.380
SHE DIDN'T SEEM TOO HAPPY
TO SEE ME THEN, EITHER.

12:40.380 --> 12:42.512
DOES SHE HATE COPS
OR SOMETHING?

12:42.512 --> 12:45.765
NO, JUST, UH, IT TAKES A LOT
FOR HER TO ASK FOR HELP.

12:45.765 --> 12:47.097
SO, LET'S NOT
MAKE HER ASK.

12:47.097 --> 12:49.649
I'LL HAVE A COUPLE
BLACK AND WHITES DRIVE BY TODAY.

12:49.649 --> 12:51.191
FOR PEACE OF MIND.

12:53.733 --> 12:56.776
I'M GUESSING YOU'RE PLANNING
ON DRIVING ONE OF THEM.

12:56.776 --> 12:59.199
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:59.199 --> 13:01.822
ARE YOU GONNA TELL ME
THAT YOU'RE NOT TRYING
TO IMPRESS EMILY?

13:01.822 --> 13:03.783
DUDE, YOU'RE WAY OFF.

13:05.035 --> 13:07.327
IF I WANTED TO ASK EMILY OUT,
I'D ASK HER OUT.

13:08.909 --> 13:11.081
BUT I'M STARTING TO
FEEL LIKE YOU'D HAVE
A PROBLEM WITH THAT.

13:13.083 --> 13:14.584
[ SIGHS ]

13:14.584 --> 13:18.128
LISTEN, MAN. I'M JUST TRYING
TO UNCOMPLICATE THINGS WITH HER.

13:19.589 --> 13:21.131
THAT'S ALL
YOU HAD TO SAY.

13:21.131 --> 13:23.844
ALL RIGHT.
MESSAGE RECEIVED.

13:23.844 --> 13:25.685
LOUD AND CLEAR.

13:32.272 --> 13:35.275
[ BELL DINGS ]

13:40.991 --> 13:42.032
MAY I HELP YOU?

13:42.032 --> 13:43.573
NO. SORRY.

13:55.505 --> 13:57.007
Cashier:
I SAW THAT.

14:00.050 --> 14:01.591
WHAT?

14:05.725 --> 14:07.137
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY!

14:07.807 --> 14:11.181
[ GRUNTING LOUDLY ]
 STAY DOWN.

14:11.181 --> 14:12.022
LET ME GO.

14:12.022 --> 14:13.773
Officer:
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

14:13.773 --> 14:15.645
[ GROANING ]

14:23.693 --> 14:26.116
Woman: YEAH.
 THIS SHOULD DO IT.

14:26.116 --> 14:27.577
THANK YOU.

14:38.258 --> 14:41.841
HEY, TOWNSEND,
WHO'S THE PERP?

14:41.841 --> 14:43.883
SOME "JOHN DOE"
KELLER AND I PICKED UP.

14:43.883 --> 14:45.805
MISDEMEANOR SHOPLIFTING.

14:45.805 --> 14:48.098
AND HE WAS TWO SECONDS AWAY
FROM ADDING RESISTING ARREST.

14:48.098 --> 14:50.010
YEAH. THAT HOW
HE GOT THE LIMP?

14:50.010 --> 14:51.932
NOPE. LOOKS LIKE
IT'S THE ONE THING

14:51.932 --> 14:53.603
HE BROUGHT
INTO THE STORE WITH HIM.

14:53.603 --> 14:54.644
SO, NO WEAPONS?

14:54.644 --> 14:56.066
OR I.D.

14:56.066 --> 14:58.728
WE STILL HAVE TO RUN HIS PRINTS
THROUGH THE NATIONAL DATABASE.

14:58.728 --> 15:00.320
LOOKS LIKE A GUY
WITH A RECORD A MILE LONG.

15:00.320 --> 15:02.612
THAT'S CALLED PROFILING,
YOU KNOW?

15:02.612 --> 15:04.114
WELL, WHO DIED
AND MADE YOU A LIBERAL?

15:19.129 --> 15:20.961
[ Ringing ]

15:20.961 --> 15:23.383
EMILY: Hey, you've called Emily.
Leave a message.

15:23.383 --> 15:24.965
[ BEEP ]
 YEAH, EMILY, IT'S BEN.

15:24.965 --> 15:26.506
IF YOU HAVE TIME,
COME DOWN TO THE STATION.

15:26.506 --> 15:28.048
I THINK WE MAY
HAVE SOMETHING.

15:28.048 --> 15:32.892
♪ ON THE SURFACE,
I LET IT COME APART ♪

15:32.892 --> 15:35.895
[ SONG CONTINUES ]

15:35.895 --> 15:38.018
MAY I SIT?

15:38.018 --> 15:40.940
DOES MY ANSWER MATTER?

15:40.940 --> 15:41.821
HAS IT EVER?

15:41.821 --> 15:44.324
YES.

15:44.324 --> 15:47.067
WHAT YOU AND CHARLOTTE THINK
MATTERS TO ME.

15:47.067 --> 15:49.869
FOR ALL THE MOTHERING
I THOUGHT I'D DONE,

15:49.869 --> 15:51.071
I FAILED YOU BOTH,

15:51.071 --> 15:53.283
AND I'M GOING TO SPEND
THE REST OF MY LIFE

15:53.283 --> 15:54.624
TRYING TO REMEDY THAT.

15:54.624 --> 15:57.247
BUT FOR NOW...

15:57.247 --> 16:01.001
PLEASE ALLOW ME TO OFFER
SOME FINANCIAL SUPPORT.

16:07.297 --> 16:08.508
WHERE'D YOU
GET THIS?

16:08.508 --> 16:10.140
WELL, AS I TOLD YOU,

16:10.140 --> 16:13.353
YOUR FATHER WAS A MASTER
AT HIDING ASSETS, SO...

16:13.353 --> 16:14.644
THAT SHOULD BE ENOUGH

16:14.644 --> 16:16.016
TO KEEP YOU AND CHARLOTTE
AFLOAT FOR A WHILE.

16:16.016 --> 16:19.019
WELL, AS LONG AS MARGAUX
DOESN'T MAKE YOU REPAY IT.

16:19.019 --> 16:22.602
MAN, YOU COME WITH OPEN ARMS
AND NOTHING BUT LIES.

16:24.654 --> 16:28.158
MARGAUX WAS KIND ENOUGH
TO OFFER.

16:28.158 --> 16:29.279
WE'RE PRACTICALLY FAMILY.

16:29.279 --> 16:30.450
YEAH, BUT YOU'RE NOT.

16:30.450 --> 16:34.994
FINALLY, THE SILVER LINING
IN PASCAL'S DEATH.

16:34.994 --> 16:36.456
OH, YOU'RE BEING CRUEL,

16:36.456 --> 16:39.039
AND IF WE WERE NOT
IN SUCH A PUBLIC PLACE,

16:39.039 --> 16:41.381
I WOULD SMACK YOUR MOUTH.

16:41.381 --> 16:43.293
YOU WILL NOT SPEAK ILL
OF PASCAL AGAIN.

16:43.293 --> 16:44.384
LIKE YOU SAID,

16:44.384 --> 16:46.216
I'M THE PATRIARCH
OF THIS FAMILY --

16:46.216 --> 16:48.007
I'LL SAY WHAT I WANT.

16:50.090 --> 16:51.221
DO ME A FAVOR --

16:51.221 --> 16:54.224
STAY AWAY FROM MARGAUX,
AND STAY AWAY FROM CHARLOTTE.

16:54.224 --> 16:58.768
AS FOR ME,
WELL, IT SHOULD BE CLEAR.

16:58.768 --> 17:00.980
Waiter:
MRS. GRAYSON...

17:00.980 --> 17:03.733
LA TOUR 1928 FOR YOU
FROM A SECRET ADMIRER.

17:03.733 --> 17:04.483
NO, THANKS.

17:04.483 --> 17:06.646
I WAS JUST LEAVING.

17:15.994 --> 17:20.500
I'M SORRY, MS. ELLIS,
BUT MRS. GRAYSON DECLINED.

17:20.500 --> 17:23.292
WELL, DID YOU TELL HER
IT WAS LA TOUR 1928?

17:23.292 --> 17:24.584
AS YOU REQUESTED.

17:24.584 --> 17:26.005
[ SIGHS ]

17:26.005 --> 17:28.088
THIS WAS A STUPID IDEA!

17:28.088 --> 17:30.130
Waiter: THE GESTURE
WAS LOVELY.

17:30.130 --> 17:31.010
[ SCOFFS ] YEAH.

17:31.010 --> 17:33.473
A GLASS FROM
A $20,000 BOTTLE OF CHAMPS

17:33.473 --> 17:35.135
IS MORE
THAN LOVELY, DEAR.

17:36.846 --> 17:37.727
[ SIGHS ]

17:37.727 --> 17:39.389
YOU ENJOY IT.

17:39.389 --> 17:41.101
THANKS.
 YEAH.

17:43.103 --> 17:44.184
[ SIGHS ]

17:44.184 --> 17:48.318
WELL, WHO NEEDS CHAMPAGNE?

17:52.992 --> 17:55.115
AT NO POINT
DURING THE LINEUP

17:55.115 --> 17:58.788
ARE YOU TO ATTEMPT COMMUNICATION
OF ANY KIND WITH ANYONE.

17:58.788 --> 18:00.370
STEP FORWARD ONLY WHEN
YOUR NUMBER IS CALLED.

18:00.370 --> 18:01.371
ARE WE CLEAR?

18:04.504 --> 18:06.085
HEAD UP,
NUMBER THREE.

18:12.842 --> 18:13.973
David.

18:20.770 --> 18:22.222
FILE THEM OUT.

18:29.028 --> 18:31.191
[ Dialing ]

18:31.191 --> 18:33.193
YOU OKAY, PORTER?

18:33.193 --> 18:34.364
YEAH.

18:34.364 --> 18:36.496
YEAH, NO, I JUST FINISHED,
UH, PREPPING THE LINEUP.

18:36.496 --> 18:38.238
NOW I GOT TO --
I GOT TO GO.

18:38.238 --> 18:40.039
YOU NEED
TO GET THIS ONE RIGHT.

18:40.039 --> 18:42.662
A BREAK-IN AT THE GRAYSON MANOR
WILL SET OFF PANIC ALARMS,

18:42.662 --> 18:44.294
AND THE LAST THING
WE NEED

18:44.294 --> 18:46.546
IS A RASH OF UNSOLVED
HOME INVASIONS.

18:46.546 --> 18:47.627
RIGHT.
YES, SIR.

18:47.627 --> 18:49.629
YOU TOOK THE INITIAL
STATEMENT, CORRECT?

18:49.629 --> 18:50.960
YES.
UM, YEAH.

18:50.960 --> 18:52.922
TAKE A MINUTE.
FILL ME IN.

18:54.304 --> 18:55.305
[ SIGHS ]

18:55.305 --> 18:57.177
YEAH, LET ME
CALL YOU BACK.

18:57.177 --> 18:58.518
HI. I'M GLAD
YOU COULD MAKE IT.

18:58.518 --> 18:59.969
I LEFT WORD
FOR MR. ROSS, AS WELL.

18:59.969 --> 19:01.221
YOU'RE THE FIRST
TO ARRIVE.

19:01.221 --> 19:02.222
YOU GUYS WORK FAST.

19:02.222 --> 19:03.853
WELL, A GUY MATCHING
YOUR DESCRIPTION

19:03.853 --> 19:05.144
CAME IN
ON ANOTHER CASE.

19:05.144 --> 19:06.186
HE EVEN HAD
A LEG INJURY.

19:06.186 --> 19:07.937
SO, WE THOUGHT
IT WAS WORTH A LOOK.

19:07.937 --> 19:09.439
SO, YOU WERE
JUST LUCKY?

19:09.439 --> 19:11.401
OR INCREDIBLY SKILLFUL.

19:12.902 --> 19:14.324
LOOK, IF WE DO
FIND THE INTRUDER,

19:14.324 --> 19:16.075
COULD YOU PLEASE
TELL YOUR PARTNER

19:16.075 --> 19:18.448
TO CALL OFF THE SQUAD CAR
PARKED OUTSIDE OF MY HOUSE?

19:18.448 --> 19:20.450
WELL, I COULD,
BUT I SENT IT.

19:20.450 --> 19:22.702
LOOK. I KNOW YOU'RE NO
DAMSEL IN DISTRESS, ALL RIGHT?

19:22.702 --> 19:24.123
I WAS JUST
TRYING TO GIVE YOU

19:24.123 --> 19:25.955
SOME PEACE OF MIND
AFTER A TRAUMATIC NIGHT.

19:25.955 --> 19:27.207
WELL, THANK YOU,
BUT I --

19:27.207 --> 19:27.997
YEAH, I KNOW --

19:27.997 --> 19:31.961
YOU CAN TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF.

19:31.961 --> 19:34.794
I KEEP FORGETTING
THAT YOU WERE IN JUVIE.

19:36.386 --> 19:39.178
WE'RE FOLLOWING UP
WITH MR. ROSS AND MS. THORNE --

19:39.178 --> 19:40.350
MS. THORNE.

19:40.350 --> 19:42.602
CHIEF ALVAREZ.

19:42.602 --> 19:44.394
WE'VE ACTUALLY MET.

19:44.394 --> 19:47.267
RIGHT, AT MY WEDDING.
VICTORIA INVITED YOU.

19:47.267 --> 19:49.108
WELL, I'LL LET YOU
GET TO IT.

19:49.108 --> 19:51.271
TRUST ME,
YOU'RE IN CAPABLE HANDS.

19:51.271 --> 19:54.113
THANKS, CHIEF.
 THANKS.

19:54.113 --> 19:55.275
SO, WE GOOD?

19:55.275 --> 19:58.117
BEN, I NEED TO SPEAK
WITH EMILY FOR A MINUTE.

19:58.117 --> 19:58.988
ALONE.

19:58.988 --> 20:00.950
WHAT, ARE YOU
FORGETTING PROTOCOL?

20:00.950 --> 20:03.533
YOU PREPPED THE LINEUP,
YOU CAN'T SPEAK TO THE
WITNESS IN PRIVATE.

20:03.533 --> 20:06.376
A FIRST-YEAR LAW STUDENT
WOULD HAVE THAT I.D.
TOSSED AT TRIAL.

20:06.376 --> 20:07.997
COME ON.
YOU TALK TO HER AFTER.

20:15.134 --> 20:16.756
Ben:
ALL RIGHT. BRING THEM OUT.

20:20.009 --> 20:22.011
NOW, EMILY, I KNOW
YOU ONLY CAUGHT A GLIMPSE.

20:22.011 --> 20:24.764
JUST --
JUST TAKE YOUR TIME.

20:40.780 --> 20:43.162
NUMBER THREE.

20:46.075 --> 20:48.458
NUMBER THREE,
STEP FORWARD.

21:19.359 --> 21:21.030
[ SNIFFLES ]

21:23.202 --> 21:24.954
[ SIGHS ]

21:26.326 --> 21:27.407
EM.

21:27.407 --> 21:30.119
THERE'S NO REASON
TO BE INTIMIDATED.

21:30.119 --> 21:32.121
ALL RIGHT?
HE CAN'T SEE YOU.

21:32.121 --> 21:33.753
I know.

21:35.965 --> 21:37.507
ARE YOU READY
TO MAKE AN I.D.?

21:39.218 --> 21:40.760
No.

21:40.760 --> 21:42.422
IT'S NOT HIM.

21:42.422 --> 21:46.185
JUST TAKE YOUR TIME.

21:46.185 --> 21:48.057
I'M SURE.

21:51.100 --> 21:53.353
I DON'T RECOGNIZE ANYONE.

21:57.777 --> 21:58.988
♪ I DON'T WANT ANOTHER LOVER ♪

21:58.988 --> 22:02.442
♪ SO DON'T KEEP
HOLDING OUT YOUR HANDS ♪

22:04.073 --> 22:06.616
♪ THERE'S NO ROOM BESIDE ME ♪

22:06.616 --> 22:08.077
♪ I'M NOT LOOKING FOR ROMANCE ♪

22:08.077 --> 22:10.209
YOU STILL CHECKING OUT
MY PORTFOLIO?

22:12.622 --> 22:15.214
YOU CAN AFFORD
TO TAKE SOME MORE RISKS.

22:15.214 --> 22:18.047
YOUR BUYS HAVE BEEN
WAY TOO CONSERVATIVE.

22:18.047 --> 22:20.299
SAYS THE GUY
IN A SUIT AT A POOL.

22:20.299 --> 22:23.723
COME ON. IT'S SUMMER,
IT'S HOT AS HELLFIRE.

22:23.723 --> 22:26.225
DON'T YOU WANT
TO GET IN AND COOL OFF,

22:26.225 --> 22:28.057
THEN WE CAN TALK
SOME BUSINESS?

22:28.057 --> 22:31.270
I'D RATHER TALK ABOUT
INCREASING YOUR RETURN.

22:31.270 --> 22:33.643
I COULD GIVE YOU
SOME QUICK FIXES,

22:33.643 --> 22:36.355
BUT YOU NEED A MORE
COMPREHENSIVE OVERHAUL.

22:36.355 --> 22:37.567
TRUST ME.

22:39.939 --> 22:41.401
AND WHY
SHOULD I TRUST YOU?

22:41.401 --> 22:43.653
I DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT YOU --

22:43.653 --> 22:45.745
EXCEPT FOR
YOUR LAST NAME.

22:45.745 --> 22:47.987
WELL, DON'T HOLD THAT
AGAINST ME.

22:47.987 --> 22:49.288
TABLOIDS PRINT LIES.

22:49.288 --> 22:51.290
MM.
MY BROTHER'S IN POLITICS --

22:51.290 --> 22:53.413
I'M AWARE OF HOW PAPERS
ARE SOLD.

22:53.413 --> 22:54.704
IT'S ALL LIES AND SEX.

22:54.704 --> 22:59.168
WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME
SOMETHING ABOUT YOURSELF?

22:59.168 --> 23:02.301
SOMETHING PERSONAL,
LIKE, UM...

23:02.301 --> 23:04.303
TELL ME
ABOUT YOUR MOTHER.

23:04.303 --> 23:07.136
SAYS A LOT ABOUT
A MAN'S CHARACTER,

23:07.136 --> 23:09.098
HOW HE GETS ALONG
WITH HIS MAMA.

23:09.098 --> 23:12.391
WELL, WE DON'T HAVE
THE BEST RELATIONSHIP.

23:12.391 --> 23:13.773
WHY?

23:13.773 --> 23:15.895
SHORT ANSWER --

23:15.895 --> 23:17.146
SHE MEDDLES.

23:17.146 --> 23:19.569
[ SIGHS ]
WELL, AT LEAST SHE CARES.

23:19.569 --> 23:21.981
I WASN'T EVEN WORTH MEDDLING
TO MY MOTHER.

23:21.981 --> 23:25.575
I WENT NEVER GOOD ENOUGH,
SMART ENOUGH, OR PRETTY ENOUGH.

23:25.575 --> 23:29.078
ONE TIME,
WHEN I WAS 14,

23:29.078 --> 23:31.030
I PUT A "HEX" ON HER
TO MAKE HER LOVE ME.

23:31.030 --> 23:32.742
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

23:32.742 --> 23:33.793
DID IT WORK?

23:33.793 --> 23:35.124
OH, NO, DARLIN'.

23:35.124 --> 23:37.416
NOTHING CAN FIX
THE DEVIL.

23:37.416 --> 23:39.378
MY MAMA AND I,
WE'LL NEVER MEND THINGS,

23:39.378 --> 23:41.961
BUT [SIGHS]

23:41.961 --> 23:46.716
I'D GIVE ANYTHING TO START OVER
WITH A GREAT MOM, YOU KNOW?

23:46.716 --> 23:50.259
WELL, MAYBE
WE'RE BETTER OFF.

23:52.101 --> 23:53.973
SO, TELL ME --

23:53.973 --> 23:55.014
WHAT DOES YOUR MAMA
MEDDLE WITH?

23:55.014 --> 23:56.896
THAT'S A STORY
FOR ANOTHER DAY.

23:58.107 --> 24:00.820
BUT YOU CAN
TRUST ME, OKAY?

24:00.820 --> 24:03.773
I WANT TO MAKE YOU
A LOT OF MONEY, LOUISE.

24:03.773 --> 24:07.827
THE QUESTION IS,
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

24:09.569 --> 24:11.280
TELL YOU WHAT --

24:11.280 --> 24:14.283
HOW ABOUT I TEST YOUR NASDAQ
PICKS WHILE YOU HELP ME OUT?

24:19.999 --> 24:22.041
I NEED TO KNOW
YOU HAVE MY BACK.

24:24.253 --> 24:27.346
♪ ALL I WANT ♪

24:27.346 --> 24:31.591
♪ IS TO ONE DAY COME TO KNOW ♪

24:35.184 --> 24:37.687
Nolan: HEY, I JUST
GOT BEN'S MESSAGE.

24:37.687 --> 24:39.519
WHAT'S IS HAPPENING?
WHAT IS GOING ON?

24:39.519 --> 24:41.020
[ CRYING, PANTING ]

24:41.020 --> 24:43.192
EMS?

24:43.192 --> 24:44.233
EM?

24:44.233 --> 24:49.068
BABE, YOU'RE
FREAKING ME OUT.

24:49.068 --> 24:50.489
WHAT HAPPENED?

24:50.489 --> 24:51.611
EMS?

24:53.783 --> 24:55.745
MY FATHER...

24:55.745 --> 24:57.376
HE'S ALIVE.

24:57.376 --> 25:00.039
WHAT -- WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?
 I JUST SAW HIM
IN THE LINEUP.

25:00.039 --> 25:01.210
BUT...

25:01.210 --> 25:02.171
NO, NO, NO.
NO, NO.

25:02.171 --> 25:04.003
I SWEAR TO GOD, NOLAN.
IT WAS HIM!

25:05.625 --> 25:07.336
NO...

25:07.336 --> 25:09.839
HOW IS THIS POSSIBLE?

25:09.839 --> 25:11.681
AFTER EVERYTHING I...

25:13.182 --> 25:14.974
IT WAS HIM, NOLAN --

25:14.974 --> 25:16.305
IN MY HOUSE LAST NIGHT.
IT HAD TO HAVE BEEN.

25:16.305 --> 25:17.897
BUT WHY -- WHY WOULD HE
BREAK INTO MY HOUSE?

25:17.897 --> 25:18.978
WHY WOULD HE WANT
TO HURT ME?

25:18.978 --> 25:20.099
I DON'T KNOW.
I -- I DON'T KNOW.

25:20.099 --> 25:21.060
EM.

25:21.060 --> 25:22.982
WHAT THE HELL, MAN?
IS THIS REAL?

25:25.645 --> 25:27.947
IT IS.

25:27.947 --> 25:29.949
HIS FINGERPRINTS JUST CAME BACK
FROM THE D.O.J.

25:29.949 --> 25:32.572
HE WAS ARRESTED
ON THE EDGE OF TOWN.

25:32.572 --> 25:35.364
HE WAS BRUISED
AND DISORIENTED.

25:35.364 --> 25:38.117
JACK...

25:38.117 --> 25:39.248
PLEASE.
I NEED TO SEE HIM.

25:39.248 --> 25:41.040
I'LL FIND A WAY.

25:41.040 --> 25:42.792
[ Shakily ] OKAY.

25:42.792 --> 25:44.333
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

25:49.128 --> 25:53.633
WHAT IS THIS ABOUT,
EDWARD?

25:53.633 --> 25:56.265
I'M SORRY TO HAVE BROUGHT YOU
IN HERE LIKE THIS, VICTORIA.

25:56.265 --> 25:58.137
I HEARD YOU WERE BACK
IN THE CITY,

25:58.137 --> 25:59.769
SO I HAD THE NYPD
ON THE LOOKOUT.

25:59.769 --> 26:02.561
WELL, YOUR OFFICERS SNEAK ME
THROUGH THE BACK ENTRANCE?

26:02.561 --> 26:04.183
[ CHUCKLES ]
AM I IN TROUBLE?

26:04.183 --> 26:05.524
NO.
NO, NOT AT ALL.

26:05.524 --> 26:06.946
GIVEN OUR LONG HISTORY,

26:06.946 --> 26:09.148
I THOUGHT A FACE-TO-FACE
MIGHT BE BEST...

26:09.148 --> 26:11.030
BEFORE THE STORY BREAKS.

26:11.030 --> 26:13.192
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
HAVE A SEAT.

26:15.154 --> 26:18.077
MY OFFICERS
ARRESTED A MAN TODAY

26:18.077 --> 26:20.660
WHOSE PRINTS CAME BACK
AS THOSE OF DAVID CLARKE.

26:20.660 --> 26:24.043
I KNOW THIS MUST BE SHOCKING
TO YOU, TO SAY THE LEAST.

26:24.043 --> 26:26.335
YOUR HEAD MUST BE SPINNING
WITH A THOUSAND QUESTIONS,

26:26.335 --> 26:28.758
BUT TRUST ME,
WE'LL GET ANSWERS.

26:28.758 --> 26:32.171
WHAT DID HE SAY?
WHERE HAS HE BEEN?

26:32.171 --> 26:34.263
WELL, UNFORTUNATELY,
MR. CLARKE ISN'T SPEAKING,

26:34.263 --> 26:36.846
BUT THE INVESTIGATION AS TO
HIS WHEREABOUTS THESE PAST YEARS

26:36.846 --> 26:37.847
IS UNDER WAY,

26:37.847 --> 26:39.478
AS WELL AS
A POSSIBLE CONNECTION

26:39.478 --> 26:41.430
TO A BREAK-IN
IN YOUR FORMER RESIDENCE.

26:41.430 --> 26:42.772
NOW, LISTEN, VICTORIA.

26:42.772 --> 26:44.603
I DON'T WANT
TO FRIGHTEN YOU,

26:44.603 --> 26:47.857
BUT YOU MAY HAVE BEEN
THE INTENDED VICTIM.

26:47.857 --> 26:50.489
I'M SORRY.

26:52.992 --> 26:54.233
[ SIGHS ]

26:54.233 --> 26:56.656
TH-THIS IS ALL
A BIT MUCH.

26:56.656 --> 26:58.327
COULD I, UM...

26:58.327 --> 27:00.449
COULD I HAVE
A MOMENT ALONE, PLEASE?
 SURE.

27:00.449 --> 27:02.832
I'LL GET YOU
SOME WATER.

27:12.011 --> 27:14.593
Nolan: DO YOU KNOW WHAT YOU'RE
GONNA SAY TO YOUR FATHER?

27:14.593 --> 27:15.755
NO.
[ SNIFFLES ]

27:16.926 --> 27:17.887
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

27:21.761 --> 27:23.062
IT'S TOO LATE.

27:23.062 --> 27:24.223
No, it's not.

27:24.223 --> 27:25.644
YOU CLEARED HIS NAME,
HE IS A FREE MAN,

27:25.644 --> 27:26.605
THEY CANNOT HOLD HIM.

27:26.605 --> 27:28.147
THEY CAN IF HE
ESCAPED FROM PRISON,

27:28.147 --> 27:29.068
IF HE FAKED
HIS OWN DEATH.

27:29.068 --> 27:30.229
AND WHAT ABOUT
LAST NIGHT?

27:30.229 --> 27:31.771
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

27:31.771 --> 27:33.322
EMS, NO!

27:33.322 --> 27:35.194
SORRY. THE PRECINCT'S
SHUTTING DOWN. NO VISITORS.

27:35.194 --> 27:36.275
I-I'M NOT A VISITOR.

27:36.275 --> 27:38.327
I'M, UH, I'M HERE
TO SEE OFFICER PORTER.

27:38.327 --> 27:40.199
MA'AM, DO WE HAVE
A PROBLEM?

27:40.199 --> 27:42.992
WELL, I GUESS THE NEWS IS OUT
ABOUT DAVID CLARKE.

27:42.992 --> 27:45.164
MS. THORNE HERE WAS
ONE OF THE FIRST TO
SEE HIM IN A LINEUP.

27:45.164 --> 27:46.085
I JUST WANT ANSWERS.

27:46.085 --> 27:48.377
OFFICER, ESCORT HER
OUT OF HERE.

27:48.377 --> 27:51.711
LOOK. I KNOW YOU WANT
TO GET IN THERE AND SEE
HIM FOR YOUR FRIEND.

27:51.711 --> 27:52.922
I'M STARTING TO THINK

27:52.922 --> 27:55.174
IT'S WHAT KEPT YOU
FROM MAKING AN I.D. EARLIER.

27:55.174 --> 27:57.676
ALL RIGHT, WE HAVE TO
LET THE FEDS HANDLE THIS,

27:57.676 --> 27:59.969
AND THERE'S NOTHING YOU CAN DO
RIGHT NOW EXCEPT WAIT,

27:59.969 --> 28:02.431
SO JUST GO HOME,
PLEASE.

28:04.804 --> 28:06.515
AMANDA WOULDN'T
WANT ME TO.

28:06.515 --> 28:09.568
EMS...

28:09.568 --> 28:10.770
IT'S TIME TO GO.

28:10.770 --> 28:13.112
LET'S GO HOME.

28:13.112 --> 28:14.864
PLEASE.

28:14.864 --> 28:15.905
PLEASE.

28:29.708 --> 28:31.831
LOUISE SENT OVER
A NICE LITTLE RETAINER

28:31.831 --> 28:33.542
INTO MY ACCOUNT
THIS AFTERNOON,

28:33.542 --> 28:37.006
SO I AM BACK IN BUSINESS
AND BACK IN THE PENTHOUSE.

28:37.006 --> 28:41.220
THE CONCIERGE EVEN SENT UP SOME
CHAMPAGNE TO WELCOME ME BACK.

28:41.220 --> 28:43.142
MARGAUX: You can be
very persuasive.

28:43.142 --> 28:44.844
WELL, I MAY NEED YOU

28:44.844 --> 28:48.187
TO HELP ME WOO A FEW
AWARD-WINNING JOURNALISTS

28:48.187 --> 28:49.769
OVER TO LEMARCHAL.

28:49.769 --> 28:52.111
AH, YOU'RE A ROCKSTAR, BABE.
YOU DON'T NEED MY HELP.

28:52.111 --> 28:53.522
I want to hear
about everything.

28:53.522 --> 28:56.355
WHAT ABOUT LOUISE?
WHAT IS SHE LIKE?

28:56.355 --> 28:59.068
HOW ABOUT YOU SWING BY LATER
FOR DINNER?

28:59.068 --> 29:00.990
I'LL TELL YOU
ALL ABOUT IT.

29:00.990 --> 29:02.361
I WOULD LOVE THAT.

29:02.361 --> 29:03.412
UNTIL THEN.

29:03.412 --> 29:04.493
ALL RIGHT.

29:07.286 --> 29:08.457
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

29:11.630 --> 29:12.631
LOUISE.

29:12.631 --> 29:14.043
I THOUGHT WE WERE DONE
FOR THE DAY.

29:14.043 --> 29:15.044
Louise:
OH, WE ARE.

29:15.044 --> 29:18.507
I SAW YOU
CHECK IN EARLIER.

29:18.507 --> 29:20.049
I'M IN PENTHOUSE A,
REMEMBER?

29:20.049 --> 29:22.091
RIGHT.
RIGHT.

29:22.091 --> 29:23.762
AND I THOUGHT

29:23.762 --> 29:26.645
WE MIGHT BE ABLE TO CELEBRATE
OUR NEW PARTNERSHIP IN PERSON.

29:28.017 --> 29:30.099
IT'S LA TOUR 1928.

29:30.099 --> 29:32.231
MY MOTHER
LOVES THE STUFF.

29:32.231 --> 29:37.196
D-DID YOU SEND OVER A GLASS
TO MY MOM EARLIER?

29:37.196 --> 29:38.397
NO, WHY?

29:38.397 --> 29:42.241
IT'S JUST THAT, UH,
THAT'S HER FAVORITE, TOO.

29:42.241 --> 29:44.703
[ Chuckling ]
OH, WELL...

29:44.703 --> 29:46.205
YOU KNOW, THEY SAY,

29:46.205 --> 29:49.038
"COINCIDENCE IS GOD'S WAY
OF STAYING ANONYMOUS."

29:49.038 --> 29:54.083
AND MEETING YOU WAS DEFINITELY
DIVINE INTERVENTION.

29:54.083 --> 29:56.085
NOW, I KNOW THIS SOUNDS
HIPPY DIPPY AND ALL,

29:56.085 --> 30:01.090
BUT I SWEAR IF YOU JUST ASK
THE UNIVERSE FOR SOMETHING,

30:01.090 --> 30:03.843
MOST OF THE TIME, IT WILL
JUST LAND RIGHT IN YOUR LAP.

30:03.843 --> 30:05.925
WELL,
I'LL REMEMBER THAT.

30:05.925 --> 30:09.348
OH, BEFORE I FORGET,
I HAVE ONE MORE THING FOR YOU.

30:09.348 --> 30:10.429
CLOSE YOUR EYES.

30:10.429 --> 30:11.560
HMM?

30:11.560 --> 30:12.731
DO IT.

30:16.986 --> 30:18.107
Okay. Open.

30:20.399 --> 30:23.072
RULE NUMBER ONE --

30:23.072 --> 30:24.573
NO MORE SUITS.

30:24.573 --> 30:25.654
RULE NUMBER TWO --

30:25.654 --> 30:27.867
IF WE'RE GOING TO BE
WORKING TOGETHER,

30:27.867 --> 30:30.709
I'M GONNA NEED YOU TO SQUEEZE IN
A LITTLE PLAY TIME.

30:30.709 --> 30:33.002
MAYBE BY THE POOL?

30:33.002 --> 30:34.833
UNLESS...

30:34.833 --> 30:36.215
YOU HAVE A PROBLEM
WITH THAT?

30:37.216 --> 30:38.217
NOT AT ALL.

30:38.217 --> 30:41.380
GREAT!
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:41.380 --> 30:42.761
AH...

30:42.761 --> 30:45.174
AND TO THINK I ALMOST DIDN'T
WALK INTO THAT BAR LAST NIGHT.

30:48.057 --> 30:49.308
WELL, OKAY.

30:49.308 --> 30:51.020
YOU ENJOY YOUR CHAMPAGNE.

30:53.392 --> 30:54.143
TOODLES.

30:54.143 --> 30:55.895
[ Chuckling ] TOODLES.

30:57.316 --> 30:59.028
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

31:02.151 --> 31:04.443
[ SIGHS ]

31:10.449 --> 31:12.291
Stiegel:
MR. CLARKE...

31:12.291 --> 31:16.085
I'M AGENT STIEGEL WITH THE
FEDERAL BUREAU OF INVESTIGATION.

31:16.085 --> 31:18.877
THIS INTERVIEW
IS BEING RECORDED.

31:18.877 --> 31:19.999
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

31:22.671 --> 31:23.963
I'M SUSAN LUKE.

31:23.963 --> 31:25.925
I'VE BEEN RETAINED
TO REPRESENT MR. CLARKE.

31:25.925 --> 31:27.886
RETAINED BY WHOM?

31:27.886 --> 31:28.677
[ SIGHS ]

31:30.139 --> 31:31.720
OH...

31:31.720 --> 31:32.771
VICTORIA.

31:32.771 --> 31:33.973
GET HER OUT OF HERE.
NOW.

31:33.973 --> 31:36.145
ACTUALLY, I'D LIKE YOU ALL
TO CLEAR THE ROOM.

31:36.145 --> 31:38.317
MR. CLARKE HAS THE RIGHT
TO CONFER WITH COUNSEL.
 I DON'T NEED THAT.

31:38.317 --> 31:40.980
MR. CLARKE --
 I JUST WANT
TO TELL THE TRUTH.

31:42.321 --> 31:43.572
IT'S ALL
I HAVE LEFT.

31:44.693 --> 31:47.076
I'M NOT A TERRORIST.

31:47.076 --> 31:49.408
I WAS FRAMED...

31:49.408 --> 31:51.120
AND TAKEN
FROM MY DAUGHTER.

31:51.120 --> 31:53.162
I WAS STABBED
IN PRISON,

31:53.162 --> 31:55.204
BUT I DIDN'T DIE.

31:55.204 --> 31:59.418
CONRAD GRAYSON --
HE FAKED MY DEATH,

31:59.418 --> 32:02.881
AND THEN HE
LOCKED ME AWAY FOR YEARS.

32:02.881 --> 32:04.173
[ SCOFFS ]

32:04.173 --> 32:06.425
I WAS TORTURED.

32:06.425 --> 32:07.886
I...

32:07.886 --> 32:10.259
PLEASE CONTINUE,
MR. CLARKE.

32:11.550 --> 32:15.144
CONRAD,
HE PAID GUARDS

32:15.144 --> 32:19.728
JUST TO CRUSH
ANY HOPE THAT I HAD LEFT.

32:21.981 --> 32:25.194
I SAW A CHANCE TO RUN.
I TOOK IT.

32:25.194 --> 32:27.026
AND THAT'S
WHEN I WAS ARRESTED.

32:27.026 --> 32:30.489
BUT I KNOW THAT...

32:30.489 --> 32:33.662
CONRAD WILL --
WILL FIND ME.

32:33.662 --> 32:34.743
HE'LL KILL ME.

32:36.575 --> 32:39.418
MR. CLARKE, CONRAD GRAYSON
CANNOT HURT YOU.

32:39.418 --> 32:42.581
[ CHUCKLES ] HE'S EVIL.
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

32:42.581 --> 32:44.083
DAVID,
CONRAD IS DEAD.

32:45.584 --> 32:48.757
HE WAS KILLED
SIX MONTHS AGO.

32:48.757 --> 32:53.802
BEFORE HE DIED,
HE ADMITTED...

32:53.802 --> 32:55.184
TO FRAMING YOU.

32:55.184 --> 32:56.975
YOUR NAME
HAS BEEN CLEARED.

32:56.975 --> 32:59.688
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

32:59.688 --> 33:01.810
[ LAUGHS ]

33:01.810 --> 33:03.362
NOW, MR. CLARKE,

33:03.362 --> 33:06.985
WE'RE GONNA NEED YOU
TO LEAD US TO WHERE
MR. GRAYSON KEPT YOU.

33:06.985 --> 33:08.027
YEAH.

33:08.027 --> 33:10.109
Stiegel:
CAN YOU DO THAT?
 Y-YEAH. YEAH.

33:10.109 --> 33:11.820
YEAH.
I THINK I CAN.

33:11.820 --> 33:15.074
I'D LIKE TO REQUEST
THAT MR. CLARKE BE RELEASED.

33:15.074 --> 33:17.826
THE GOVERNMENT WILL NEED
TO VET HIS VERSION OF EVENTS.

33:17.826 --> 33:18.617
OF COURSE.

33:18.617 --> 33:19.828
BUT I ASSURE YOU

33:19.828 --> 33:22.251
THAT MR. CLARKE
IS NOT A FLIGHT RISK.

33:22.251 --> 33:25.003
THIS IS A BROKEN
AND FRIGHTENED MAN

33:25.003 --> 33:26.925
WHO WILL COOPERATE
WITH THIS INVESTIGATION.

33:26.925 --> 33:32.341
PLEASE, LET HIM
COME HOME...

33:32.341 --> 33:34.183
WITH ME.

33:38.016 --> 33:39.308
[ SIGHS ]

33:39.308 --> 33:41.730
[ INDISTINCT REPORTING
ON TELEVISION ]

33:54.032 --> 33:56.455
ARE THEY REPORTING
ANYTHING YET?

33:56.455 --> 33:58.367
NO.

33:59.958 --> 34:01.920
LISTEN...

34:04.463 --> 34:05.544
[ SIGHS ]

34:05.544 --> 34:09.007
AFTER I LOST MY DAD...

34:11.550 --> 34:16.175
...ALL I EVER WISHED FOR WAS
JUST TO SEE HIM ONE MORE TIME.

34:18.637 --> 34:22.601
I'D SETTLE
FOR FIVE MINUTES...

34:22.601 --> 34:24.233
ONE MORE
KISS GOOD NIGHT.

34:26.185 --> 34:27.396
YOUR WISH CAME TRUE.

34:27.396 --> 34:30.449
GOD, I CAN'T WRAP MY HEAD
AROUND ANY OF THIS.

34:35.694 --> 34:37.996
Reporter: I BELIEVE
WE HAVE SOME BREAKING NEWS.

34:37.996 --> 34:39.197
EMS. LOOK.

34:39.197 --> 34:40.789
WE JOIN
CHIEF EDWARD ALVAREZ NOW.

34:40.789 --> 34:42.791
Reporter #2: DO YOU HAVE
DAVID CLARKE IN CUSTODY?

34:42.791 --> 34:44.081
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

34:44.081 --> 34:48.337
IT IS TRUE
THAT DAVID CLARKE IS ALIVE.

34:48.337 --> 34:50.168
IN HIS FIRST STATEMENT,

34:50.168 --> 34:53.342
MR. CLARKE REPORTS THAT HE
WAS HELD BY CONRAD GRAYSON,

34:53.342 --> 34:56.304
BEATEN AND TORTURED
FOR 10 YEARS.

34:56.304 --> 35:00.599
ALTHOUGH HIS ASSERTION IS STILL
SUBJECT TO CONFIRMATION,

35:00.599 --> 35:06.024
THE FBI HAS DECIDED TO RELEASE
DAVID CLARKE ON GOOD FAITH.

35:06.024 --> 35:09.027
AFTER THIS 20-YEAR ORDEAL,

35:09.027 --> 35:11.069
DAVID CLARKE
IS FINALLY A FREE MAN.

35:11.069 --> 35:14.613
HE'S EXPECTED TO MAKE A PUBLIC
STATEMENT WITHIN THE NEXT HOUR.

35:14.613 --> 35:17.035
[ SIGHS ] MY GOD.
 THAT'S IT. NO QUESTIONS.
THANK YOU.

35:17.035 --> 35:21.160
I KNEW CONRAD WAS EVIL,
BUT THIS...

35:21.160 --> 35:23.081
I SHOULD HAVE
KILLED HIM MYSELF.

35:23.081 --> 35:24.082
EMS, BREATHE.

35:24.082 --> 35:26.124
I'M GOING DOWN THERE.

35:26.124 --> 35:27.876
I NEED TO SEE
MY DAD TONIGHT.

35:27.876 --> 35:30.048
I KNOW YOU WANT TO,
BUT NOT LIKE THIS.

35:30.048 --> 35:34.132
EMS, NOT IN PUBLIC.
YOU BOTH DESERVE SO MUCH MORE.

35:34.132 --> 35:38.016
WE DESERVED MORE
20 YEARS AGO.

35:38.016 --> 35:40.018
I CAN'T WAIT
ONE MORE DAY.

35:48.267 --> 35:50.189
CHARLOTTE'S ON HER WAY DOWN.
SHE'S WORRIED SICK.

35:50.189 --> 35:51.820
THE WAY THE NEWS
IS REPORTING THIS,

35:51.820 --> 35:53.111
THEY ASSUME
YOU'RE FRAGILE.

35:53.111 --> 35:54.983
I'M NOT.

35:54.983 --> 35:57.035
I KNOW.

35:57.035 --> 35:59.828
IN THAT INTERROGATION ROOM,

35:59.828 --> 36:02.120
I REMEMBERED THE MAN
I FELL IN LOVE WITH --

36:02.120 --> 36:05.284
SMART, A RISK TAKER,

36:05.284 --> 36:08.086
A MAN WHO WAS WILLING
TO GO TO ANY LENGTHS

36:08.086 --> 36:09.748
TO DO WHAT
YOU DID TODAY,

36:09.748 --> 36:12.551
TO FINALLY REVEAL
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM.

36:12.551 --> 36:15.133
DAVID...

36:18.467 --> 36:20.429
...YOU KNOW YOU CAN
TELL ME ANYTHING.

36:23.802 --> 36:26.475
WHEN I WAS LOCKED AWAY,

36:26.475 --> 36:30.729
I ANALYZED EVERYTHING...

36:30.729 --> 36:32.020
EVEN YOU.

36:33.232 --> 36:35.484
DO YOU REMEMBER
HOW I WANTED US TO LEAVE

36:35.484 --> 36:37.866
WEEKS BEFORE I WAS ARRESTED
FOR FLIGHT 197

36:37.866 --> 36:41.079
AND YOU SAID, "LET ME
TAKE CARE OF THINGS"?

36:42.581 --> 36:45.494
THIS MORNING,
YOU SAID THE SAME THING.

36:47.165 --> 36:49.037
I WON'T BE ANYONE'S
PRISONER ANYMORE...

36:50.499 --> 36:52.090
...NOT EVEN YOURS,
VICTORIA.

36:53.962 --> 36:56.755
YOU GRABBED ME,
AND I STAYED.

36:56.755 --> 36:58.677
I NEVER
HELD YOU HOSTAGE.

36:58.677 --> 37:00.759
I WAS TRYING
TO KEEP YOU SAFE.

37:00.759 --> 37:03.392
YOU HAD SIX MONTHS
OF UNACCOUNTED-FOR TIME,

37:03.392 --> 37:06.765
AND I AM NEVER GOING
TO LET YOU GO DOWN
FOR CONRAD'S DEATH.

37:09.898 --> 37:11.690
THAT'S WHY
I RETAINED A LAWYER --

37:11.690 --> 37:14.152
A BETTER LAWYER
THAN YOU AND I CAN AFFORD.

37:15.564 --> 37:19.488
I DID IT FOR YOU.

37:19.488 --> 37:20.779
FOR US.

37:20.779 --> 37:22.451
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

37:22.451 --> 37:25.864
MR. CLARKE, WE'RE READY
TO PROCESS YOUR RELEASE.

37:25.864 --> 37:27.746
OH. [ SIGHS ]

37:31.710 --> 37:33.542
YOU STILL
NEED ME, DAVID.

37:35.253 --> 37:38.176
AND I WILL ALWAYS
NEED YOU.

37:43.972 --> 37:45.304
DAVID?

37:51.810 --> 37:54.232
Margaux: SO, I JUST GOT YOU
ALL TO MYSELF

37:54.232 --> 37:57.446
AND NOW I HAVE TO SHARE YOU
WITH YOUR THIS NEW CLIENT?

37:59.818 --> 38:02.030
OH, IS SOMEBODY
JEALOUS?

38:02.030 --> 38:02.991
WHO?

38:02.991 --> 38:04.453
ME? NO.
 YEAH, YOU'RE JEALOUS.

38:04.453 --> 38:06.615
OH, NO, I'M NOT.
NO, NO.

38:06.615 --> 38:07.666
NO?
 NO.

38:07.666 --> 38:09.117
WELL, THAT'S TOO BAD.

38:09.117 --> 38:09.958
WHY?

38:09.958 --> 38:11.670
'CAUSE I KIND OF
LIKE IT.

38:11.670 --> 38:14.673
[ CELLPHONE CHIMING ]

38:21.840 --> 38:22.921
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

38:22.921 --> 38:25.013
[ SIGHS ]

38:25.013 --> 38:27.806
FIRE WHOEVER'S
ON THAT PHONE.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

38:30.519 --> 38:32.140
MARGAUX LEMARCHAL.

38:34.232 --> 38:36.525
IS IT CONFIRMED?

38:36.525 --> 38:39.027
OKAY, RUN IT IMMEDIATELY,
ALL MEDIA OUTLETS.

38:39.027 --> 38:41.149
AND WE NEED A PRESENCE
AT THAT PRESS CONFERENCE.

38:41.149 --> 38:44.032
Reporter: HE NOW SAYS
HIS MURDER WAS A SMOKESCREEN.

38:44.032 --> 38:47.325
CONRAD GRAYSON
KIDNAPPED HIM IN PRISON...
 WHAT THE HELL?

38:47.325 --> 38:50.288
...AND THEN HELD HIM IN A SILO
ON A REMOTE GRAYSON PROPERTY.
 IT'S DAVID CLARKE.

38:50.288 --> 38:53.832
MR. CLARKE HAS AGREED
TO COOPERATE WITH THE FBI...
 HE'S ALIVE.

38:53.832 --> 38:55.414
...AS THEY CONTINUE
TO INVESTIGATE

38:55.414 --> 38:57.335
HIS HARROWING STORY.

38:57.335 --> 39:00.048
MR. CLARKE IS EXPECTED
TO MAKE A PUBLIC STATEMENT

39:00.048 --> 39:01.129
IN JUST A FEW MINUTES.

39:05.343 --> 39:07.225
HEY, YOU ALL RIGHT, MAN?

39:07.225 --> 39:08.096
YEAH.

39:08.096 --> 39:10.769
YEAH. SORRY FOR FREAKING OUT
IN THE LINEUP.

39:10.769 --> 39:12.521
WHAT,
ARE YOU KIDDING?

39:12.521 --> 39:15.394
COME ON. THAT GUY'S
YOUR FATHER-IN-LAW, RIGHT?

39:15.394 --> 39:18.817
LOOK, I UNDERSTAND,
BUT YOU SHOULD'VE FILLED ME IN.

39:18.817 --> 39:20.068
I KNOW. I'M SORRY.

39:20.068 --> 39:21.149
I JUST, UH...

39:21.149 --> 39:23.071
THOUGHT MAYBE
I WAS SEEING THINGS

39:23.071 --> 39:25.073
UNTIL I SAW
EMILY'S REACTION.

39:25.073 --> 39:26.905
YEAH, WELL,
SHE'S PRETTY UPSET.

39:26.905 --> 39:28.076
SHE TRIED
TO GET PAST THE FEDS.

39:29.828 --> 39:32.491
SHE WANTS ANSWERS
JUST LIKE YOU, FOR AMANDA.

39:35.754 --> 39:37.706
WELL, LISTEN.
I THINK I'M GONNA --

39:37.706 --> 39:38.797
I'M GONNA GO.

39:38.797 --> 39:40.088
WHAT, NOW?

39:40.088 --> 39:41.840
BUT HE'S ABOUT
TO BE RELEASED.

39:41.840 --> 39:45.213
YOU MUST HAVE A TON
OF QUESTIONS FOR HIM.

39:45.213 --> 39:48.306
D-DON'T YOU AT LEAST
WANT TO MEET HIM

39:48.306 --> 39:49.387
AFTER ALL THIS TIME?

39:49.387 --> 39:51.219
NO.

39:51.219 --> 39:52.811
AND IF IT'S
ALL THE SAME TO YOU,

39:52.811 --> 39:54.683
I DON'T WANT HIM KNOWING
I'M ON THE FORCE YET.

39:54.683 --> 39:56.144
I'M JUST --

39:56.144 --> 39:58.066
I'M NOT READY
TO SEE HIM.

40:04.983 --> 40:06.234
AFTER HOURS
OF SPECULATION,

40:06.234 --> 40:08.366
WE ARE NOW MOMENTS AWAY
FROM A LIVE STATEMENT

40:08.366 --> 40:10.198
FROM THE MAN
FORMERLY FOUND GUILTY

40:10.198 --> 40:12.120
OF ONE OF THE MOST HEINOUS
ACTS OF TERROR

40:12.120 --> 40:13.371
THIS COUNTRY
HAS EVER SEEN.

40:13.371 --> 40:16.334
GIVEN HIS SENSATIONAL
AND SURPRISING TALE

40:16.334 --> 40:18.036
OF THE PAST 10 YEARS,

40:18.036 --> 40:20.589
IT IS SAFE TO SAY
DAVID CLARKE, ONCE HATED,

40:20.589 --> 40:23.211
MAY NOW BE THE NEW SYMBOL
OF HOPE AND COURAGE.

40:27.305 --> 40:30.308
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

40:38.937 --> 40:40.228
THANK YOU
FOR COMING.

40:40.228 --> 40:42.400
I'M HERE FOR HIM,
NOT YOU.

40:42.400 --> 40:44.693
I-I PRAYED
FOR THIS MOMENT,

40:44.693 --> 40:46.565
THIS FREEDOM,

40:46.565 --> 40:49.738
AND TODAY, UH,
MY PRAYERS WERE ANSWERED.

40:49.738 --> 40:52.621
AND I NEVER IMAGINED
SEEING THIS KIND OF SUPPORT

40:52.621 --> 40:54.783
FROM A PUBLIC
WHO HAD CONDEMNED ME

40:54.783 --> 40:58.376
AND A FAMILY THAT I THOUGHT
HAD FORGOTTEN ABOUT ME.

40:58.376 --> 40:59.918
HE SHOULDN'T
BE UP THERE ALONE.

40:59.918 --> 41:01.289
NO, NO, NO.
JUST WAIT.

41:09.387 --> 41:11.049
VICTORIA...

41:11.049 --> 41:13.011
CHARLOTTE...

41:13.011 --> 41:14.392
PLEASE JOIN ME?

41:21.099 --> 41:22.981
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

41:25.483 --> 41:28.316
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

41:28.316 --> 41:29.868
Reporter:
MRS. GRAYSON,

41:29.868 --> 41:32.160
SEEMS YOUR FAMILY CAN'T ESCAPE
THE GHOSTS OF THE PAST.

41:32.160 --> 41:36.164
CHARLOTTE AND I
ARE FOCUSED ON THE FUTURE...

41:36.164 --> 41:38.877
AND GETTING TO KNOW DAVID
ONCE AGAIN.

41:38.877 --> 41:40.879
DAVID HAS BEEN
THROUGH A --

41:40.879 --> 41:42.250
A HORRIFIC EXPERIENCE

41:42.250 --> 41:45.213
AT THE HANDS
OF MY LATE EX-HUSBAND,

41:45.213 --> 41:48.216
CONRAD GRAYSON,
WHO WAS AN EVIL, EVIL MAN.

41:48.216 --> 41:52.050
WE ALL NEED TIME
TO UNDERSTAND AND TO PROCESS.

41:52.050 --> 41:55.223
WE ASK FOR PRIVACY
AT THIS MOMENT

41:55.223 --> 41:56.725
SO THAT DAVID
COULD READJUST

41:56.725 --> 42:00.098
AND TO BE
WITH LOVED ONES...

42:00.098 --> 42:01.349
AND HIS FAMILY.

42:01.349 --> 42:02.641
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

42:04.062 --> 42:06.645
THAT'S ALL
THE QUESTIONS FOR NOW.

42:13.742 --> 42:15.363
WHAT JUST HAPPENED?

42:15.363 --> 42:18.206
[ SIGHS ]

42:18.206 --> 42:22.000
SHE GOT TO HIM FIRST.
